OL,4,Cpatients
OL,6,FAt least 392 patients treated by
OL,7,Fmental health services in England
OL,8,Fcommitted, or were suspected of,
OL,9,Fmurder or manslaughter between 2018
OL,10,Fand 2023.
OL,12,FThe Health Secretary, Wes Streeting,
OL,13,Fhas described the findings as
OL,14,F"horrifying", telling ITV News he will
OL,15,Fwatch the problem like a "hawk".
