OL,3,CHundreds killed by NHS mental health
OL,4,Cpatients
OL,6,FThe findings come after an independent
OL,7,Freport exposed a series of NHS
OL,8,Ffailures in the treatment of Valdo
OL,9,FCalocane, a man with schizophrenia who
OL,10,Fkilled three people in Nottingham in
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,FAlthough many cases don't make
OL,14,Fnational headlines, this data confirms
OL,15,Fthere are dozens of families bereaved
OL,16,Fby mental health killings in England
OL,17,Fevery year.
OL,19,F"Our family has been through hell."
