OL,6,FRoger Leadbeater's family are
OL,7,Ftraumatised by his death.
OL,9,F"I still have sleepless nights. I get
OL,10,Freally bad anxiety," Roger's great-
OL,11,Fniece, Ellie Hector, told ITV News.
OL,13,FRoger, who worked as bus driver for
OL,14,Fchildren with special needs, was
OL,15,Fattacked as he walked his dog in
OL,16,FSheffield in August 2023.
OL,18,FThe 74-year-old was stabbed more than
OL,19,F70 times by a woman who had escaped
OL,20,Ffrom a secure mental health hospital
OL,21,Fin Bolton days earlier.
