OL,6,FEmma Borowy, 32, had been diagnosed
OL,7,Fwith schizophrenia and sectioned under
OL,8,Fthe Mental Health Act, but absconded
OL,9,Ffrom psychiatric hospital 10 times in
OL,10,Feight months.
OL,12,FShe was violent and had been found
OL,13,Fwith knives, and yet NHS staff allowed
OL,14,Fher out on escorted leave, just days
OL,15,Fafter a previous escape.
OL,17,FThe family of Roger Leadbeater, who
OL,18,Fwas killed by a woman who had escaped
OL,19,Ffrom a secure mental health hospital,
OL,20,Ftells ITV News they have "been through
OL,21,Fhell" following his death
