OL,6,F"We are more angry towards the
OL,7,Fservices that we feel let her down,
OL,8,Fthat's what caused Roger's death,"
OL,9,FRoger's niece, Angela Hector, told ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,FEmma Borowy died in prison while
OL,13,Fawaiting trial.
OL,15,FRoger's family says "justice" can only
OL,16,Fbe served through an improvement to
OL,17,Fmental health services.
OL,19,F"The buck stops with the NHS because
OL,20,Fthey shouldn't have let her out," said
OL,21,FEllie Hector.
