OL,6,F"There is pressure on the NHS but I
OL,7,Fdon't think people were doing their
OL,8,Fjobs properly."
OL,10,FSalli Midgley, Chief Nurse at Greater
OL,11,FManchester Mental Health NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust, told ITV News: "Our
OL,13,Fthoughts and sympathies remain with
