OL,6,FThe vast majority of people who are
OL,7,Fmentally ill are not violent, but some
OL,8,Fpeople who are severely ill will need
OL,9,Fto be detained under the Mental Health
OL,10,FAct to protect themselves and others
OL,11,Ffrom harm.
