OL,6,FJulian Hendy founded the charity
OL,7,FHundred Families to support those
OL,8,Fbereaved by homicides carried out by
OL,9,Fmentally ill people.
OL,11,FHis 75-year-old father was killed by a
OL,12,Fman with a long history of mental
OL,13,Fhealth problems.
OL,15,F"I loved my dad, he was funny, he was
OL,16,Fkind, he was a great man - and he
OL,17,Fdidn't deserve to die in the way he
OL,18,Fdid," Julian told ITV News.
