OL,6,FWhen Julian discovered a lack of
OL,7,Fofficial statistics, he decided to
OL,8,Fcarry out the research himself.
OL,10,F"A lot of people who die are children
OL,11,For are elderly and vulnerable, that is
OL,12,Fnot acceptable. Somebody has to stand
OL,13,Fup and try and do something."
