OL,4,Cpatients
OL,6,FFreedom of Information requests were
OL,7,Fsent to 50 NHS Mental Health Trusts in
OL,8,FEngland, asking for the number of
OL,9,Fpatients who had committed, or were
OL,10,Fsuspected of committing, a homicide,
OL,11,Fbetween 2018 and 2023 - including
OL,12,Fcommunity and hospital patients,
OL,13,Feither current or those who had been
OL,14,Fin contact with services within six
OL,15,Fmonths of the offence.
OL,17,F48 Trusts responded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
