OL,4,Cpatients
OL,6,FSome NHS Trusts did not reveal the
OL,7,Fexact numbers, only that there had
OL,8,Fbeen less than five to six cases a
OL,9,Fyear, so the charity was able to
OL,10,Fcalculate minimum and maximum figures.
OL,12,FAt least 392 mental health patients in
OL,13,FEngland killed people during the six
OL,14,Fyears, an average of 65 a year. But
OL,15,Fthe number could be up to 508, an
OL,16,Faverage of 85 a year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
