OL,6,FEven this is an underestimate of the
OL,7,Ftrue scale, as it doesn't include
OL,8,Fthose unwilling or unable to access
OL,9,Fmental health services and people,
OL,10,Flike Valdo Calocane, who killed his
OL,11,Fvictims more than six months after any
OL,12,Fcontact with mental health services.
OL,14,F"It shouldn't be down to me as a
OL,15,Fgrieving, bereaved family member and a
OL,16,Fcharity worker to come up with this
OL,17,Fdata," Julian Hendy said.
OL,19,F"Why is nobody in authority collecting
OL,20,Fthis properly?
