OL,6,F"If you're not counting the numbers
OL,7,Fcorrectly, how can you start to deal
OL,8,Fwith the problem?"
OL,10,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting ITV
OL,11,FNews' findings as "horrifying"
OL,13,FITV News showed the findings to the
OL,14,FHealth Secretary, Wes Streeting, who
OL,15,Fdescribed the numbers as "horrifying".
OL,17,FThe government has promised to reform
OL,18,Fmental health laws in England and
OL,19,FWales to give patients more "dignity
OL,20,Fand say over their care".
