OL,6,FThe Mental Health Bill is currently
OL,7,Fmaking its way through parliament.
OL,9,FStreeting told ITV News MPs were
OL,10,F"looking really carefully" at the
OL,11,Fbalance between the freedoms of people
OL,12,Fwho are mentally ill and the potential
OL,13,Frisk they pose to themselves or
OL,14,Fmembers of the public.
OL,16,F"The commitment I can give to the
OL,17,Ffamilies who are going through
OL,18,Funimaginable grief", said the Health
OL,19,FSecretary, "is that the practice in
OL,20,Fthe NHS is already changing and
OL,21,Flessons... are being applied."
